  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000B.agda" type="external">erct-000B.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
                  </fr:frontmatter>
                  <fr:mainmatter>
                    <html:p>A <html:em><html:strong>precategory</html:strong></html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> is specified by the following data:</html:p>
                    <html:ol><html:li>a type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert C\right \rvert \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> of <html:em>objects</html:em>, written <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[c\in  C]]></fr:tex>;</html:li>
  <html:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x,y\in  C]]></fr:tex> a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001J/" title="Sets" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001J/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001J" type="local">set</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> of <html:em>arrows</html:em>, written <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  x\to  y]]></fr:tex>;</html:li>
  <html:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  C]]></fr:tex>, an <html:em>identity arrow</html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[1_{x}\colon  x\to  x]]></fr:tex>;</html:li>
  <html:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  x\to  y]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\colon  y\to  z]]></fr:tex>, a <html:em>composite arrow</html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\circ  f\colon  x \to  z]]></fr:tex>;</html:li>
  <html:li>such that composition is associative and unital with respect to identity arrows:
    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
      \boldsymbol {\lambda }_{f}\colon  1_{y}\circ  f = f\quad 
      \boldsymbol {\rho }_{f}\colon  f\circ  1_{x} = f \quad 
      \boldsymbol {\alpha }_{f,g,h}\colon  
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen h\circ  g\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\circ  f = h\circ 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen g\circ  f\right \rparen \mathclose {}

    ]]></fr:tex></html:li></html:ol>
                  </fr:mainmatter>
                </fr:tree>
                <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
                  <fr:frontmatter>
                    <fr:authors>
                      <fr:author>
                        <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                      </fr:author>
                    </fr:authors>
                    <fr:date>
                      <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
                      <fr:month>12</fr:month>
                      <fr:day>3</fr:day>
                    </fr:date>
                    <fr:uri>https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000I/</fr:uri>
                    <fr:display-uri>https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000I</fr:display-uri>
                    <fr:route>/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000I/</fr:route>
                    <fr:title text="Functor between precategories">Functor between <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B/" title="Precategory" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B" type="local">precategories</fr:link></fr:title>
                    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
                    <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000I.agda" type="external">erct-000I.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
                  </fr:frontmatter>
                  <fr:mainmatter>
                    <html:p>A <html:em><html:strong>functor</html:strong></html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F\colon  C\to  D]]></fr:tex> from a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B/" title="Precategory" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B" type="local">precategory</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> to a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B/" title="Precategory" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000B" type="local">precategory</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> is defined by the following data:</html:p>
                    <html:ol><html:li>a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert F\right \rvert \mathclose {}
\colon  
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert C\right \rvert \mathclose {}
\to 
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert D\right \rvert \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> giving the <html:em>action of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex> on objects</html:em>, where we shall write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Fx]]></fr:tex> for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert F\right \rvert \mathclose {}
x]]></fr:tex> given <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  C]]></fr:tex>;</html:li>
  <html:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x,y\in  C]]></fr:tex> a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F_{x,y} \colon  C
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
 \to  D
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen Fx,Fy\right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> giving the <html:em>action of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex> on arrows</html:em>, where we shall write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Ff\colon  Fx\to  Fy]]></fr:tex> for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F_{x,y}f]]></fr:tex> given <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  x\to  y]]></fr:tex>;</html:li>
  <html:li>such that the action on morphisms commutes with identities and compositions:
    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
      F^{1_{x}}\colon  F1_{x} = 1_{Fx}\quad 
      F^{g\circ  f}\colon  F
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen g\circ  f\right \rparen \mathclose {}
 = Fg\circ  Ff
    ]]></fr:tex></html:li></html:ol>
                  </fr:mainmatter>
                </fr:tree>
                <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
                  <fr:frontmatter>
                    <fr:authors>
                      <fr:author>
                        <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                      </fr:author>
